parser

Class SlideData

  • java.lang.Object
    • parser.SlideData

  • public class SlideData
extends java.lang.Object
    This class creates a new object of type SlideData. It contains the title and duration of a single slide, and lists containing all the TextData, ImageData, AudioData, VideoData, & GraphicData objects on this slide.
    Version:
    2.1
    Author:
    Copyright (c) 2015 EyeHouse Ltd. All rights reserved.
